hands_on_practices.solution:
算符为 $\hat{S}=\alpha \hat{\sigma}_{x}+\beta \hat{\sigma}_{y}$，因此根据线性性质，
$$
\hat{S}\hat{\sigma}_{z}=\alpha\,\hat{\sigma}_{x}\hat{\sigma}_{z}+\beta\,\hat{\sigma}_{y}\hat{\sigma}_{z},\qquad
\hat{\sigma}_{z}\hat{S}=\alpha\,\hat{\sigma}_{z}\hat{\sigma}_{x}+\beta\,\hat{\sigma}_{z}\hat{\sigma}_{y}.
$$
使用标准的泡利矩阵，
$$
\hat{\sigma}_{x}\hat{\sigma}_{z}
=\begin{pmatrix}0  1\\ 1  0\end{pmatrix}\begin{pmatrix}1  0\\ 0  -1\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}0  -1\\ 1  0\end{pmatrix},\quad
\hat{\sigma}_{y}\hat{\sigma}_{z}
=\begin{pmatrix}0  -i\\ i  0\end{pmatrix}\begin{pmatrix}1  0\\ 0  -1\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}0  i\\ i  0\end{pmatrix}.
$$
因此，
$$
\hat{S}\hat{\sigma}_{z}
=\alpha\begin{pmatrix}0  -1\\ 1  0\end{pmatrix}
+\beta\begin{pmatrix}0  i\\ i  0\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}0  -\alpha+i\beta\\ \alpha+i\beta  0\end{pmatrix}.
$$
类似地，
$$
\hat{\sigma}_{z}\hat{\sigma}_{x}
=\begin{pmatrix}1  0\\ 0  -1\end{pmatrix}\begin{pmatrix}0  1\\ 1  0\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}0  1\\ -1  0\end{pmatrix},\quad
\hat{\sigma}_{z}\hat{\sigma}_{y}
=\begin{pmatrix}1  0\\ 0  -1\end{pmatrix}\begin{pmatrix}0  -i\\ i  0\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}0  -i\\ -i  0\end{pmatrix},
$$
所以
$$
\hat{\sigma}_{z}\hat{S}
=\alpha\begin{pmatrix}0  1\\ -1  0\end{pmatrix}
+\beta\begin{pmatrix}0  -i\\ -i  0\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}0  \alpha-i\beta\\ -\alpha-i\beta  0\end{pmatrix}.
$$
根据定义，$\hat{M}=\hat{S}\hat{\sigma}_{z}-\hat{\sigma}_{z}\hat{S}$，因此
$$
\hat{M}
=\begin{pmatrix}0  -\alpha+i\beta\\ \alpha+i\beta  0\end{pmatrix}
-\begin{pmatrix}0  \alpha-i\beta\\ -\alpha-i\beta  0\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}0  -2\alpha+2i\beta\\ 2\alpha+2i\beta  0\end{pmatrix}.
$$
因此，第一行第二列的元素是
$$
M_{12}=-2\alpha+2i\beta.
$$
